metadata.name: THE JACKAL
metadata.description:
The Jackal is part of our original Resin and Mixed media Art Collection called Assassin-Nation.

Each of our skulls has been inspired by an infamous movie character Assassin.

The Jackal is based on Bruce Willis's character The Jackal, in the movie of the same title involving murder and assassination between the FBI, the MVD and a mob leader with The Jackal as the ruthless professional hitman.

The artwork itself is resin in midnight blue, white and silver with silver metallic powder encased in a 30mm silver pearl steel frame. It has stunning clear Swarovski crystals as its face which you can see sparkling in the image.

The artwork measures 1150mm x 720mm.

The winner of this NFT gets the original artwork itself, shipped worldwide from Australia.
